quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,94,"(aur Aey Musalmaano) tum apni kasamon ko aapas mein ek dusre ko dhoka dene ka zariya na bana lena, kahin aisa na ho ke koi qadam jamne ke baad ukhad jaye aur tum is jurm ki padash mein ke tumne logon ko Allah ki raah se roka, bura nateeja dekho aur sakht saza bhugto"
  16,95,"Allah ke ahad ko thode se faiyde ke badle na bech daalo (sell off/barter away), jo kuch Allah ke paas hai woh tumhare liye zyada behtar hai agar tum jaano"
  16,96,"Jo kuch tumhare paas hai woh kharch ho janey wala hai aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai wahi baaqi rehne wala hai, aur hum zaroor sabr se kaam lene walon ko unke ajar unke behtareen aamaal ke mutaabiq denge"
  16,97,"Jo shaks bhi neik amal karega, khwa woh mard ho ya aurat, bashart ye ke ho woh momin, usey hum duniya mein pakeeza zindagi basar karayenge aur (aakhirat mein) aisey logon ko unke ajar unke behtareen aamaal ke mutabiq bakshenge"
  16,98,Phir jab tum Quran padhne lago to Shaytan e rajeem (accursed) se khuda ki panaah maang liya karo
  16,99,Usey un logon par tasallut (power/authority) hasil nahin hota jo iman latey aur apne Rubb par bharosa karte hain
  16,100,Uska zoar to unhi logon par chalta hai jo usko apna sarparast banate aur uske behkane se shirk karte hain
  16,101,Jab hum ek ayat ki jagah dusri aayat nazil karte hain Allah behtar jaanta hia ke woh kya nazil karey to yeh log kehte hain ke tum yeh Quran khud ghadte ho. Asal baat yeh hai ke in mein se aksar log haqeeqat se na-waqif hain
  16,102,Insey kaho ke isey to rooh-ul-quddus ne theek theek mere Rubb ki taraf se ba-tadreej nazil kiya hai taa-ke iman laney walon ke iman ko pukhta karey aur farma-bardaron ko zindagi ke maamlaat mein seedhi raah bataye aur unhein falaah o saadat ki khush khabri de